U,\hat{U} \in \mathbb{R}^{n \times m}
m < n
\hat{U}_\perp \in \mathbb{R}^{n \times (n-m)}
\hat{U}
range(\hat{U})
\mathbb{R}^n
||\hat{U}^\top Ux||_2 = ||x||_2 \sqrt{1 - ||\hat{U}^\top_\perp U||^2_2}
n=3,\,m=2
\|\hat{U}^\top Ux\|_2 = \left\|\pmatrix{1\\ 0}\right\|=1
\|x\|_2 \sqrt{1 - \|\hat{U}^\top_\perp U\|^2_2}=\sqrt{1-\left\|(0,\tfrac1{\sqrt{2}})\right\|_2^2}=\sqrt{\frac12}
 U=\pmatrix{1&0\\ 0&\tfrac1{\sqrt{2}}\\ 0&\tfrac1{\sqrt{2}}}, \ \hat{U}=\pmatrix{1&0\\ 0&1\\ 0&0}, \ \hat{U}_\perp=\pmatrix{0\\ 0\\ 1}, \ x=\pmatrix{1\\ 0}. 
